    <div class='pullquote theme__text mb2 align-c'>
        <div class='mb1'>
            <p>It was possible to create a therapy — I don&#8217;t know if anyone&#8217;s ever created a therapy that quickly tested it and delivered it to a patient.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
